{"tid":1633402,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"明唔明咩叫放長線釣大魚","createTime":"2019-10-07T03:49:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T04:20:59.000Z","uid":202989,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"194a6be65a3655291c0c5e3266cc565dfa467146","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:49:45.000Z","msg":"話裝修果啲， 終有一天會裝完架。你今日裝一百間，聽日裝一百間，裝到冇得再裝唔通去裝黃店？<br />\n其實我真心真係覺得有好撚多狗煽動，好撚嬲。<br />\n唔想真手足俾人屈 俾人黑化！ 大家用個腦諗下啦。focus返係五大訴求得唔得呀！<br />\n乜都裝修私了，你地覺得同元朗白衫有冇分別？（如果係狗做既，佢地就係想手足俾人覺得係同佢地冇分別）<br />\n<br />\n我覺得好奇怪既係，裝修post有好多，負評既、唔支持既都有好多，甚至多過話支持裝修既。但點解仲係有咁多人裝修，你地諗下果啲係咩人？<br />\n<br />\n我好嬲真手足真前線俾人屈，明明佢地係好有良知，佢地係好有同情心！<br />\n<br />\n真心想講句，卧底狗係會有報應！ 仆街卧底狗！食屎狗！"},{"pid":"fecd274f3ee5a3851560991df11c2177906ac43f","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:50:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bf89e1cd64775e8a372bd33957bc345e6720de25","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:50:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"55aa13dfefae845d6cc4cc3fb0f0bbb80e4246de","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:51:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3e776b8f5e60098efcf6b26aad850350638055ae","tid":1633402,"uid":218298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:51:25.000Z","msg":"幫幫手！我地要草船借箭<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1629930\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1629930</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"eaf85bf819280129dea314fee02c0d745f34e26f","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:51:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06d287f5b7cee3edbbaf0425d93313480dc9e6e8","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:52:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf4eef9b60117fb2cd7b46e9394c769cd72218bf","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:52:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"521d5cd10876694c39fa39c22a41ff3c568e3e32","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:53:06.000Z","msg":"推 好嬲"},{"pid":"333086bb3bff2593f48109516a1bcdaf3376e551","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:53:56.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9ef3be85ec94958c405b3ca0a1bfdffb7512b1a0","tid":1633402,"uid":52621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"地產商係咪要裝修 咁多紅藍店中資 點打得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69217305f51d2a7a8f7e5d010c2037645b2fb13b","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9ef3be85ec94958c405b3ca0a1bfdffb7512b1a0","tid":1633402,"uid":52621,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:53:57.000Z","msg":"地產商係咪要裝修 咁多紅藍店中資 點打得哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:59:28.000Z","msg":"就算有中資又點。 中國夠有日資外資，大陸人又會唔會話要裝修？香港係個多元化國際城市，我地係要接受有唔同國家既企業入場，就算佢地立場係幾明顯，我地都唔可以唔接受。我地係有腦既人，唔係粗人！ 我地有學識，點解要同佢地一般見識？<br />\n香港都有好多黃店，咁藍絲裝修黃店，你地會點諗呢？<br />\n世界有好多持分者，我相信每個人都可以有自己立場，我地可以唔認同，但唔可以破壞。咁樣真係同元朗白衫冇分別。"},{"pid":"aa1b98193eb03ae939808e09e15af0f65ffb9294","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T03:59:48.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"185bff7a539932d84c56bf1bd589469767a5d317","tid":1633402,"uid":26827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:00:10.000Z","msg":"今晚唔裝修<br />\n只爆鐵<br />\n聽日三罷"},{"pid":"218d33232b9fe5f4ca0617a69cd84cade2a5e0f9","tid":1633402,"uid":120564,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:00:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"360738c045faedc4f7d57e982fe9ca8ffba509a8","tid":1633402,"uid":202989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"185bff7a539932d84c56bf1bd589469767a5d317","tid":1633402,"uid":26827,"lik